data.description: Exceptional home located in Diamond Loch of North Richland Hills. Current mortgage is assumable at 4.75 percent with lender approval. This home has recent updates including fresh interior paint, HVAC, spray foam attic insulation. Beautiful trees and landscaped lot will soon be in full bloom. The floorplan features two living areas with vaulted ceilings, built-ins, plus a wood burning fireplace. Spacious kitchen, granite countertops, double ovens, breakfast area with built-ins for additional storage. Owner's bedroom has an en-suite bathroom with double vanity, linen storage, and separate shower. Three additional bedrooms feature large closets including one split bedroom with bathroom. Fenced backyard for entertaining with a sparkling pool and includes a greenhouse for additional storage.
